%h1#object-category Category

:markdown
  `Category` is set of `MenuItem`s to organize and help user to input checkouts.

%h2#object-category-fields Fields

.row
  .span6
    %dl
      %dt= field "id", :readonly, :immutable
      %dd ID of the object.
      %dt= field "name"
      %dd Name of the item.
      %dt= field "position"
      %dd
        Position of the category in menu. <code>null</code> if the category is disabled.

  .span6
    %pre
      = preserve do
        :escaped
          {
            "id": 371,
            "name": "Coke",
            "position": 1021,
          }

%h2#get-on-menus-menu-id-categories GET on /menus/<em>menu_id</em>/categories

:markdown
  Retrieves `Category`s defined in menu specified by *menu_id*.

%h3 Request

.row
  .span6
    %pre
      = preserve do
        GET /menus/13/categories?since=2011-01-01T18:00:13Z
  .span6
    %dl
      %dt= field "since"
      %dt= field "until"
      %dt= field "glb"

%h3 Response

.row
  .span6
    %pre
      = preserve do
        :escaped
          {
            "timestamp": "2012-01-03T03:11:03Z",
            "next-url": "https://ubiregi.com/api/3/menus/13/categories?since=2011-01-01T18:00:13Z&until=2011-01-03T03:11:03Z&glb=13476",
            "last_updated_at": "2012-01-02T21:14:08Z",
            "categories": [ $categories ],
          }
  .span6
    %dl
      %dt= field "timestamp"
      %dt= field "next-url"
      %dt= field "last_updated_at"
      %dt= field "categories"

%h2#post-on-menus-menu-id-categories POST on /menus/<em>menu_id</em>/categories

:markdown
  Update/Create the categories of the menu specified by *menu_id*.

%h3 Request
.row
  .span6
    %pre
      = preserve do
        :escaped
          {
            "categories": [
              {
                "name": "Soft drinks",
                "position": 102,
              },
              {
                "id": 1022,
                "position": null,
              }
            ]
          }
  .span6
    %dl
      %dt= field "items"
      %dd
        Array of <code>Category</code> objects to be updated/created.
        %dl
          %dt= field "id"
          %dt= field "name"
          %dt= field "position", :optional

%h3 Response

.row
  .span6
    %pre
      = preserve do
        :escaped
          {
            "timestamp": "2011-11-02T09:11:12Z",
            "categories" : [ $categories ],
          }
  .span6
    %dl
      %dt= field "timestamp"
      %dt= field "categories"
